Variables : these are used to store and process the data.

types of variables.

String : to store text;
integer : these are used to store whole numbers.
character : these are used to store only alphabets
floating : these are used to store decimal values
boolean : this will store true and false



<data type> <vaiable name> = <value of the variable>;


final variables : when a variables is declared as final we cannot change the value assigned to it.
